Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:10.45,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:15.97,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}跨越数千年 接力棒传到我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:20.47,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因漫长道路而目眩 天旋地转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:26.22,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定有尚未发现的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:30.81,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}时刻都在这样思索 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:35.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不惧失败 反复尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:41.85,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哭着笑着 追寻光明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.44,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:57.21,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}又将抵达何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.70,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:06.80,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不论去何处 若没有爱 都无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:12.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Will I see you again? {\r\blur4}在道路的交点
